OL,7,FThe Borders Book Festival is underway
OL,8,Ffrom Thursday as the organisers say
OL,9,Fthe region gets set for a "glorious
OL,10,Fcelebration."
OL,12,FThe event takes place in Harmony
OL,13,FGardens in Melrose from Thursday 13
OL,14,FJune until Sunday 16 June and will
OL,15,Ffeature many big names from the
OL,16,Fworld's of literary, sport, current
OL,17,Faffairs and news.
