OL,7,FThe festival gets underway with the
OL,8,Fannouncement of the Walter Scott Prize
OL,9,Ffor Historical Fiction with six
OL,10,Fshortlisted writers vying for the
OL,11,F#25,000 prize.
OL,13,FITV broadcaster Robert Peston will be
OL,14,Fin attendance at the event, alongside,
OL,15,FClive Myrie, David Nicholls, Fred
OL,16,FMacAulay, Rory Bremner and Sally
OL,17,FMagnusson.
