OL,7,FThe book festival will also host a
OL,8,Fspecial event on the centenary of Eric
OL,9,FLiddell's 400m win at the 1924
OL,10,FOlympics.
OL,12,FFestival Director, Alistair Moffat,
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Harmony Garden stage is set
OL,14,Ffor another glorious celebration in
OL,15,Four beautiful Borders home, and we
OL,16,Fcould not be more excited to welcome
OL,17,Fold and new visitors alike to share in
OL,18,Fthe joy.
