OL,7,F"This year's book festival sees
OL,8,Ffamiliar, much-loved faces returning
OL,9,Fto our marquees to spark laughter,
OL,10,Fdebate and applause, as they do every
OL,11,Fyear, but our programme also brings
OL,12,Ftogether new voices from across the
OL,13,Fcultural spectrum, creating a truly
OL,14,Funique opportunity for exchanges of
OL,15,Fideas and the sharing of connections.
OL,17,F"Harmony Garden is where the party is
OL,18,Fat this weekend, and we don't want
OL,19,Fanybody to miss out.
