OL,7,F"There are the myriad events to
OL,8,Fexplore, but there is also the Food &
OL,9,FDrink Village in which to indulge
OL,10,Fthose summer cravings, and the
OL,11,Felectric atmosphere is added to by
OL,12,Flive music, unrivalled beauty in our
OL,13,Fsurroundings, and the reunions of
OL,14,Ffriends from far and wide in high
OL,15,Fsummer.
OL,17,F"You have to be at Harmony Garden to
OL,18,Fexperience the Borders Book Festival
OL,19,Fin all its glory.
