OL,7,F"You can't stream this on catch-up! So
OL,8,Fmake sure you're there with us to
OL,9,Fshare in the magic."
OL,11,FAlan Bett, Head of Literature &
OL,12,FPublishing at Creative Scotland said:
OL,13,F"Borders Book Festival provides an
OL,14,Fimportant and diverse literary
OL,15,Foffering to the region and beyond.
