OL,3,CBorders Book Festival to get underway
OL,4,Cas region set for 'glorious
OL,5,Ccelebration'
OL,7,F"Covering everything from cookery to
OL,8,Fcrime, politics to picture books, the
OL,9,Fprogramme caters to a broad range of
OL,10,Fliterary interests and fosters a
OL,11,Flifelong connection with books for
OL,12,Feveryone.
OL,14,F"It's particularly encouraging to see
OL,15,Fa strong focus on young readers
OL,16,Fthrough the family festival, which
OL,17,Flays essential groundwork for engaging
OL,18,Fchildren and young people in a future
OL,19,Ffilled with reading and imagination."
